                    "text": "This is the way, the Milky Way!\n\nHarvested by hand within the Hypogea, the mysterious subterranean world that extends under the Sarkans Desert, Arcolano Milk™ is one of the wonders of Asgartha. Freshly drawn from local Caecaster farms, Arcolano Milk cleanses the mind and helps you sleep well. Drinking Arcolano Milk every day fuels your imagination and promotes unbounded creativity.\n\nOverconsumption of Arcolano Milk poses a risk to health. Please drink responsibly."
